@node "Features" "Features"
TrapPrefs is an intition based preference editor for TrapDoor.

Features:
    o Supports all of the features of TrapDoor 1.84+
    o All options can be set with simple cycle gadgets, and string
      gadgets.
    o Log and Stat window sizes can be set simply by adjusting their
      size and location and clicking on a close gadget.
    o ReqTools screenmode and palette requesters.
    o Full locale support.
    o No anoying restrictions or requesters.
    o Freely distributable @{"SHAREWARE" link "shareware" 0}.
    o MUI interface.

    o For register users the follow additional features are available
         - Users of TIF can configure the Labels for the FKey gadgets

@endnode

