@node "Shareware" "Shareware"
PLEASE SUPPORT SHAREWARE!

TrapPrefs is shareware, you can set all of TrapDoor 1.84+ features in the
evauation version.  However starting with v1.3 features above those required
to configure TrapDoor will only be available in the evaulation version.

The following features which are available only in the registered version.
    o You will be able to load, edit, and save the Labels for the gadgets
      which are part of TIF.
    o You can snapshot the size and position of the window to disk

Please, if you use TrapPrefs on a regular basis, concider sending me the
registration fee.  Once I receive your registration fee I will promptly send
you a key file which will personalize and unlock your copy of TrapPrefs and
TrapListPrefs, the same keyfile works for both programs.

The following is the current price list for TrapPrefs/TrapListPrefs:
 Register with keyfile sent via e-mail:        $10.00 US.
 Register with keyfile send via regular mail:  $12.00 US. ($10 + $2 S&H)

Please see @{"Address" link "Address" 0} for how to you can reach me and where to send in your
registration fee.

